---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Wellmade" description="Wellmade's privacy policy. How we handle your data with care and transparency.">
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-title mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-body text-base mb-16">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-12 text-body leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-title mb-4">Who we are</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            This website is operated by Wellmade BV, a company incorporated under Belgian law, based in Brussels, Belgium. We can be reached at <a href="mailto:hello@wellmade.be" class="text-primary underline hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors">hello@wellmade.be</a>.
          </p>
          <p>When this policy refers to "Wellmade", "we", "us", or "our", it means Wellmade BV.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-title mb-4">What data we collect and why</h2>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-title mt-8 mb-3">Contact form</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">When you submit a message through our contact form, we collect:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-4">
            <li>Your name</li>
            <li>Your email address</li>
            <li>The content of your message</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mb-4">We use this information solely to respond to your enquiry. We do not add you to any mailing list, share your details with third parties, or use your data for any purpose beyond that conversation.</p>
          <p><strong class="text-title">Legal basis:</strong> Legitimate interest (responding to a direct enquiry you initiated).</p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-title mt-8 mb-3">Website analytics</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">We use analytics to understand how our website is used — which pages are visited, where traffic comes from, and how visitors navigate the site. This helps us improve the content and experience.</p>
          <p class="mb-4">We use Umami, a self-hosted, open-source analytics tool. All data is processed on our own infrastructure and never shared with third parties. Umami collects only aggregated, anonymised data — no cookies are used, no personal profiles are built, and no cross-site tracking occurs.</p>
          <p><strong class="text-title">Legal basis:</strong> Legitimate interest (improving our website). No consent is required because no personal data or cookies are used for this purpose.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-title mb-4">What we do not do</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We do not:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
            <li>Sell your personal data to anyone, ever</li>
            <li>Use your data for advertising or profiling</li>
            <li>Share your data with third parties, except where strictly necessary to operate our services (e.g. our email provider)</li>
            <li>Transfer your data outside the European Economic Area without appropriate safeguards</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-title mb-4">Data retention</h2>
          <p>Contact form submissions are retained only as long as necessary to handle your enquiry, and deleted afterwards. We do not maintain a long-term database of website enquiries.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-title mb-4">Your rights</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and Belgian data protection law, you have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-4">
            <li><strong class="text-title">Access</strong> the personal data we hold about you</li>
            <li><strong class="text-title">Correct</strong> inaccurate data</li>
            <li><strong class="text-title">Request deletion</strong> of your data</li>
            <li><strong class="text-title">Object</strong> to or <strong class="text-title">restrict</strong> processing in certain circumstances</li>
            <li><strong class="text-title">Lodge a complaint</strong> with the Belgian Data Protection Authority (Gegevensbeschermingsautoriteit / Autorité de protection des données) at <a href="https://www.dataprotectionauthority.be" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary underline hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors">www.dataprotectionauthority.be</a></li>
          </ul>
          <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@wellmade.be" class="text-primary underline hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors">hello@wellmade.be</a>. We will respond within 30 days.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-title mb-4">Cookies</h2>
          <p>Our website does not use cookies for tracking or advertising purposes. If we use any functional cookies (for example, to remember a language preference), these are strictly necessary and do not require your consent.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-title mb-4">Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this policy from time to time. When we do, we will update the "Last updated" date at the top of this page. We encourage you to review this page periodically.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-title mb-4">Contact</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Questions about this policy? Reach us at <a href="mailto:hello@wellmade.be" class="text-primary underline hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors">hello@wellmade.be</a>.</p>
          <p>Wellmade BV — Brussels, Belgium</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
